prod.full_name: Jordan 1 Mid Gym Red Black White
prod.path: Home/Sneakers/Air Jordan/1/Low/Jordan 1 Mid Gym Red Black White
prod.desciption:
The Air Jordan 1 Mid Gym Red Black White delivers a fresh take on the classic Chicago Bulls team colors, composed entirely of black and white leather overlays. A Gym Red Swoosh appears on each side of the sneaker with a matching embossed Gym Red Wings logo on the ankle. Lastly, a black and Gym Red Jumpman tag is stitched on the tongue.

The Air Jordan 1 Mid Gym Red Black Black White released in 2021 for $120
